0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104puj1665702585966.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/puj1665702585966.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/puj1665702585966.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"puj1665702585966\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Is Generic\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the entity or field is generic. Applicable only in modeled components.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"puj1665702585966__topic_d97307e1_d97308e1_d97309e1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"puj1665702585966__table_d10904e1_d10905e1_d10906e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Technical Name: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> GENERIC_UINHERIT </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Expected Value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Boolean </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default Value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"puj1665702585966__table_d10907e1_d10908e1_d10909e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"puj1665702585966__table_d10907e1_d10908e1_d10909e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"puj1665702585966__table_d10907e1_d10908e1_d10909e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"puj1665702585966__table_d10907e1_d10908e1_d10909e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"puj1665702585966__table_d10907e1_d10908e1_d10909e1__entry__2\"> The entity or field is generic and will be\n                        copied into derived components as a bound object. The bound object can be\n                        renamed and any ProcScript that refers to the generic object will be\n                        resolved to reference the bound object. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"puj1665702585966__table_d10907e1_d10908e1_d10909e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"puj1665702585966__table_d10907e1_d10908e1_d10909e1__entry__2\"> The entity or field is not generic. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"puj1665702585966__section_tvy_bzj_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1054234e149\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"puj1665702585966__p_d97313e1_d97314e1_d97315e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uhr1704434505611.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uhr1704434505611.html\" title=\"A modeled component is an abstract component definition that specifies a data structure, layout, and code for components that share a common purpose or similar behavior. It is used to create new components, known as derived components, which can inherit component-level changes made in the modeled component.\">Modeled Components</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"anf1704434630556.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/anf1704434630556.html\" title=\"A modeled component usually contains generic entities and fields that act as placeholders for entities and fields in the derived component.\">Generic and Bound Entities and Fields</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"puj1665702585966__section_utv_hzj_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1054234e175\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"puj1665702585966__ul_ecs_3zj_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"puj1665702585966__li_d39545e1_d39546e1_d39547e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"puj1665702585966__li_d39548e1_d39549e1_d39550e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zyj1665702550619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zyj1665702550619.html\" title=\"A Component Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Component Entity.\">Component Field</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615292\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615292\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Is Generic Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Is Generic This property determines whether the entity or field is generic. Applicable only in modeled components. Technical Name: GENERIC_UINHERIT Expected Value: Boolean Default Value: None Value Description True The entity or field is generic and will be copied into derived components as a bound object. The bound object can be renamed and any ProcScript that refers to the generic object will be resolved to reference the bound object. False The entity or field is not generic. Description For more information, see Modeled Components and Generic and Bound Entities and Fields . Applies To Component Entity Component Field Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}